rComments: I took this class in Fall 2009 with him and he was excellent! He explained everything very well, the work wasn't too difficult but wasn't boringly easy either. If he's still teaching, I highly recommend him!

Although Jesse isn't yet a professor, I thought I'd give him his first rating as an instructor... AWESOME! He is a great teacher. Not only does he know his stuff, his assignments and lectures are very well thought out, and he makes himself available for outside help. Challenging, but made possible with superior teaching skills : )
